--- title: 看病准备 updated: 2020-12-01 00:37:26Z created: 2020-12-01 00:20:20Z author: tangyongfeng@gmail.com ---
I'm a software engineer who spends most of my time working at a computer.
There are three parts of my body that make me uneasy.
1, blood pressure, I have not been concerned about blood pressure, three years ago in Beijing had been warned by the doctor. Until a week ago, I bought a blood pressure monitor and my blood pressure is sometimes very high at night. It reached 152/101 at 23:00 on November 25, and 162/100 at 8:32 on November 27.

2,Snoring, I snore very loudly, sometimes all night long. I could not sleep deeply, which made me very sleepy every day. I found out on the internet that this problem can be solv。

I don't drink alcohol, smoke about 3 e-cigarettes every day, and have no other bad habits. Maybe I've been under a lot of stress lately and stopped hiking to exercise, but I'm not feeling very well.

3,I have very bad breath and I brush my teeth very carefully every day and carry gum with me. Shortly after I eat the gum, I get bad breath, which is a serious problem for me in my work and life.
